snippet.title: Man trapped in car after crash on Kings Highway near Bungendore
snippet.content:
A single-car crash on the Kings Highway has left one man trapped and has blocked eastbound traffic on Friday morning. Police said the driver was conscious and breathing but trapped in the car near Jamaleopa Road.
Emergency services, including paramedics and firefighters, were on the scene working to free the man after receiving a call at about 7:30am. More to come.
